'\" te
.\" %W% %G%
.EQ
delim $$
.EN
.TH SCLSIZ 3F "%G%"
.SH NAME
sclsiz \- scale character sizes
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBcall sclsiz(scale)\fP
.TP 15
\fBreal*4\fP
\fBscale\fP
.SH DESCRIPTION
FORTRAN subroutine \fBsclsiz()\fP will scale character sizes up or down.
.SH ARGUMENTS
.TP 15
\fBscale\fP
.SB (i)
scale factor 
.nf
> 1.0 - scale up
= 1.0 - no scaling
< 1.0 - scale down
.SH "SEE ALSO"
\fBniceplot(3f)\fP
.SH AUTHOR
Danny Harvey
